622
00:43:31,510 --> 00:43:34,249
Catatan resmi bisa menunjukkan kapan dia pergi.

623
00:43:34,249 --> 00:43:35,649
Kuitansi juga penting.

624
00:43:36,749 --> 00:43:39,950
