Makanya bayarlah pajak. Nanti kubantu.

699
00:48:30,140 --> 00:48:32,450
Sejak kapan kamu hidup lurus?

700
00:48:34,249 --> 00:48:35,550
Setelah hidup lama,

701
00:48:37,319 --> 00:48:39,050
