734
00:52:14,970 --> 00:52:16,069
Kapan dokternya datang?

735
00:52:16,600 --> 00:52:19,410
Istri Oh Sang Do, Lee Kyung Hye. Di mana dia sekarang?

736
00:52:26,709 --> 00:52:28,649
